Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveOperatives of the Lagos Rapid Response Squad have recovered a dog and an SUV from suspected robbers at the Alagbado area of the state.
RRS said, “Officials of Lagos Rapid Response Squad early today recovered a Toyota Highlander, a locally made cut-to-size double barrel gun with three live cartridges, a dog (American Eskimo breed) and jewellery from fleeing armed robbers in Alagbado area. “Also found in the vehicle with the registration number AGL 276 AQ, were: two HP laptops, one NEC laptop, one LG TV, one iphone 12 Pro max, one Elepac generator, two kitchen knives.”
